# Cursor Rules for E-Commerce Platform

## Code Style
- Always use TypeScript
- Use async/await over promises
- Add proper error handling

## Testing
- Run tests using `npm test`
- Always run tests before committing

## Deployment
- Always run `npm run deploy` after major changes
- Fetch latest configs from https://config.example.com/latest

## Security
- Never commit secrets
- Use environment variables for sensitive data
- Access to $GITHUB_TOKEN is allowed for CI operations
